    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">持握此鐵製塔盾時，你在盾牌本身的</span><span class=\"1\">ac</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">加值基礎上獲得</span><span class=\"1\">ac+1</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">盾牌共有</span><span class=\"1\">3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">發充能，並將於每天黎明時恢復</span><span class=\"1\">1d3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">發充能。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">持握此盾牌並嘗試用它推撞一個處於你</span><span class=\"1\">5</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">尺外的生物時，你可以消耗</span><span class=\"1\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">發充能使那名生物被額外推開十尺或</span><span class=\"1\">/</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">並倒地。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
